<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="P" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Pelting" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Pelting,</orth> paltry: <cit><quote>every p. petty officer,</quote> <bibl n="shak. mm 2.2.112" default="NO" valid="yes">Meas. II, 2, 112</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>have every p. river made so proud,</quote> <bibl n="shak. mnd 2.1.91" default="NO" valid="yes">Mids. II, 1, 91</bibl></cit> (Ff <emph>petty</emph>). <cit><quote>a tenement or p. farm,</quote> <bibl n="shak. r2 2.1.60" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 II, 1, 60</bibl></cit>. <emph>we</emph> <cit><quote>have had p. wars,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tro 4.5.267" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. IV, 5, 267</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>poor p. villages,</quote> <bibl n="shak. lr 2.3.18" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. II, 3, 18</bibl></cit>.
<pb n="850" />
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>